<h1 class="post-title entry-title">Universal Nabs Rights To &#8216;Let It Snow&#8217; Short Stories Featuring Hot Author John&nbsp;Green</h1>

<div class="post-author-time">

	
	<div class="author-info coauthors">

		<span class="byline">by <a href="http://deadline.com/author/the-deadline-team/" title="Posts by The Deadline Team" rel="author" class="name">The Deadline Team</a>
		
		<div class="clear"></div></span>

		<time class="date-published updated">September 19, 2014 11:43am</time>

		<div class="clear"></div>

		<div class="counters">
	<div class="twitter" data-permalink="http://deadline.com/2014/09/let-it-snow-movie-john-green-universal-pictures-836869/" data-http-permalink="http://deadline.com/2014/09/let-it-snow-movie-john-green-universal-pictures-836869/">
